This Cloud PC was a mess. I couldn't do anything on that pathetic PC and the timer ran out. It was stuck like anything. I got 50 mbps internet !!! The videos streaming on the right side were stuck all the time, so heard nothing of that. I had to download the data set and do on my own. I complained about everything and even contacted support to give more time on that cloud pc. After that I waited for it to come but 4 days and nothing, so I just completed that graded quiz because I pretty much learned linear regression on my own without much help from this course. I guess only thing that helped was that linear regression was a very basic concept. Absolutely useless and mess of a course. Nothing is fault of the  intructor though. Never even heard his voice for more than a minute in total due to those videos getting stuck !!!

The title is appropriate - it ONLY teaches you how to do a linear regression prediction in R from a CSV file with 2 variables...Not very useful if you're interested in learning about R generally as there is no explanation given along the way as to how any of it works or why you're doing each step
The course was well presented, wish it began with a few more basics.
